Iconify PLUGIN
-------------

Constructors:
    create(label=NIL:PTR TO CHAR,icon=NIL:PTR TO CHAR)
    label - icon label (default set to '')
    icon  - name of icon file taht will be used (default 'env:sys/def_tool')

Destructor:
    END *must* be called for each NEWed object.

Action functions:
    no action function will be called

Exceptions:

    "icls" will be raised by the constructor if iconify class can't be created
    "igad" will be raised by the render() method if the gadget can't be created
    "icfy" will be raised by message_action() method
